Use the following command to send a file to the HCP
    scp "folder_path" ` s244804@transfer.gbar.dtu.dk:~/TestRepo/Data

Use the following command to send a folder to the HCP
    scp -r "folder_path" ` s244804@transfer.gbar.dtu.dk:~/TestRepo/Data

Use the following command to check available devices
    nvidia-smi

Use the following command to choose available device
    CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES= available_device, python_script.py

    CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=1 python TestHPC.py